1. Opened terminal
2. Typed sudo nano /home/pi/launcher.sh
3. input the lines:
Code: Select all

#!/bin/sh
sudo python /home/pi/Desktop/testGUI.py
4. ctrl x, y, enter.
5. in terminal, type cd /home/pi
6. type chmod 755 launcher.sh
7. type sudo nano /home/pi/.config/lxsession/LXDE-pi/autostart
8. input this into the bottom of the file
Code: Select all

@sh /home/pi/launcher.sh
9. ctrl x, y, enter.
10. sudo reboot